name: openSUSE I/O
tagline: What's going on in openSUSEs git repos
body:
### Welcome to openSUSE I/O!
This page links to all project marketing pages of things hosted in our github organization. 

* [open-build-service](https://github.com/openSUSE/open-build-service) -> http://openbuildservice.org
* [snapper](https://github.com/openSUSE/snapper) -> http://snapper.io/
* [kiwi](https://github.com/openSUSE/kiwi) -> http://en.opensuse.org/Portal:KIWI
* [osem](https://github.com/openSUSE/osem) -> http://opensuse.github.io/osem/
